p.#text:
oi( prosio/ntes e)le/fasin e)sqh=ta lampra\n ou)
 lamba/nousin, ou)de\ foiniki/das oi( tau/rois: diagriai/netai
 ga\r u(po\ tw=n xrwma/twn tou/twn ma/lista ta\ zw=|a: ta\s de\ ti/greis fasi\ peritumpanizome/nas e)kmai/nesqai panta/pasi kai\ diaspa=n e(auta/s. e)pei\ toi/nun kai\ tw=n a)ndrw=n oi( me\n e)sqh=tas kokki/nas;

kai\ porfura=s o(rw=ntes dusanasxetou=sin, oi( de\ kumba/lois kai\ tumpa/nois a)/xqontai, ti/ deino\n a)pe/xesqai tou/twn ta\s gunai=kas kai\ mh\ tara/ttein mhde\ parocu/nein tou\s a)/ndras, a)lla\ sunei=nai met' eu)staqei/as
 kai\ prao/thtos;
